<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>YeRide - Ride Smarter, Earn More</title>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 font-sans">
		<header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white py-4 fixed w-full z-10 shadow-md">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex justify-between items-center">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">YeRide</h1>
				<nav>
					<ul class="flex space-x-6">
						<li><a href="#features" class="hover:text-blue-200 transition duration-300">Features</a></li>
						<li><a href="#users" class="hover:text-blue-200 transition duration-300">For Riders</a></li>
						<li><a href="#users" class="hover:text-blue-200 transition duration-300">For Drivers</a></li>
						<li><a href="#beta" class="hover:text-blue-200 transition duration-300">Join Beta</a></li>
					</ul>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>

		<main class="pt-16">
			<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-700 text-white py-20">
				<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">Ride Smarter, Earn More with YeRide</h2>
					<p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Connecting drivers and passengers for seamless, fair-priced rides.</p>
					<div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
						<a href="#" class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-blue-100 transition duration-300 shadow-md">Download Now</a>
						<a href="#beta" class="bg-green-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-green-600 transition duration-300 shadow-md">Join Beta Testing</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="py-16 bg-white">
				<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
					<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
						<p class="text-lg mb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
							Our app revolutionizes ride sharing by connecting riders and drivers directly, ensuring lower fares for passengers and 100% earnings for drivers. Experience a service where every ride bolsters the community, not corporate profits.
						</p>
						<p class="text-lg mb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
							By cutting out the middleman and eliminating corporate profit margins, we transfer the savings directly to you. It's a win-win scenario: every journey guarantees low pricing for passengers and a better livelihood for drivers.
						</p>
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
							Join our movement where community thrives. With us, ride or drive and enjoy the benefits of a fair, transparent service - more savings for riders, more earnings for drivers.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

